   "text": "PATH A \u2014 skills generate <name> --description ...\n  LLM drafts SKILL.md, registry status: draft,\n  human reviews \u2192 PR \u2192 CI eval gate\n\nPATH B \u2014 propose_skill (auto-proposal)\n  failure clusters (trajectory.db / ab_results)\n  \u2192 draft_skill_body() \u2192 open_skill_pr()\n  branch proposal/<name>, NEVER auto-merged\n\nExport: eval/export_skill.py \u2192 Claude Code format",
   "fontSize": 12.5,
   "fontFamily": 3,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "baseline": 14,
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "PATH A \u2014 skills generate <name> --description ...\n  LLM drafts SKILL.md, registry status: draft,\n  human reviews \u2192 PR \u2192 CI eval gate\n\nPATH B \u2014 propose_skill (auto-proposal)\n  failure clusters (trajectory.db / ab_results)\n  \u2192 draft_skill_body() \u2192 open_skill_pr()\n  branch proposal/<name>, NEVER auto-merged\n\nExport: eval/export_skill.py \u2192 Claude Code format",
   "lineHeight": 1.25
  },
