   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "LangGraph + LangChain\n\nsystem_prompt = harness base_system_prompt\n  + skill.body (with_skill condition)\n\nTools (9): search_flights \u00b7 search_hotels\n  create_booking \u00b7 modify_booking \u00b7 cancel_booking\n  get_fare_rules \u00b7 check_availability\n  validate_passenger \u00b7 get_itinerary\n\nModels: gpt-4o-mini default (OPENAI_API_KEY);\n  others via OpenRouter (--model)\n\nagent_mode=orchestrated \u2192 Phase 8 router path",
   "fontSize": 12.5,
   "fontFamily": 3,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "baseline": 14,
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "LangGraph + LangChain\n\nsystem_prompt = harness base_system_prompt\n  + skill.body (with_skill condition)\n\nTools (9): search_flights \u00b7 search_hotels\n  create_booking \u00b7 modify_booking \u00b7 cancel_booking\n  get_fare_rules \u00b7 check_availability\n  validate_passenger \u00b7 get_itinerary\n\nModels: gpt-4o-mini default (OPENAI_API_KEY);\n  others via OpenRouter (--model)\n\nagent_mode=orchestrated \u2192 Phase 8 router path",
   "lineHeight": 1.25
  },
