   "text": "weighted_delta = \u03a3(\u0394\u00b7w)/\u03a3w \u2014 booking 3.0,\nflight/hotel 2.0, disruption 2.0\n\nThresholds calibrated for N=3 trials:\n  T1 BLOCK  w\u0394<\u22120.15 | crit<\u22120.30 | reg>50%\n  T2 SOFT   w\u0394<\u22120.05 | heavy<\u22120.20 | reg>35%\n  T3 WARN   small regressions   exit 0",
