   "updated": 1,
   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "python -m eval.optimizer.optimize [--cluster N] [--dry-run]\n  [--strategy ...] [--explore]\n\nTravelEnvAdapter + TravelTaskLoader plug run_task into\nskillopt 0.1.0 ReflACTTrainer (6-stage loop)\n  rollout = real eval vs mock MCP (gpt-4o-mini)\n  reflect/aggregate/select = gpt-4o\n  replacement prompts (wheel ships none)\n\nTargets:  skill \u2192 SKILL.md body (frontmatter preserved)\n          harness \u2192 ONE optimizable config key\n\nDeterministic 5:3:2 train/selection/test split\nGate: mixed (never hard at \u226410-task scale)\nHeld-out test evaluated once \u2014 the honest number\nNo improvement on test \u2192 NO proposal written",
   "fontSize": 12.5,
   "fontFamily": 3,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "baseline": 14,
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "python -m eval.optimizer.optimize [--cluster N] [--dry-run]\n  [--strategy ...] [--explore]\n\nTravelEnvAdapter + TravelTaskLoader plug run_task into\nskillopt 0.1.0 ReflACTTrainer (6-stage loop)\n  rollout = real eval vs mock MCP (gpt-4o-mini)\n  reflect/aggregate/select = gpt-4o\n  replacement prompts (wheel ships none)\n\nTargets:  skill \u2192 SKILL.md body (frontmatter preserved)\n          harness \u2192 ONE optimizable config key\n\nDeterministic 5:3:2 train/selection/test split\nGate: mixed (never hard at \u226410-task scale)\nHeld-out test evaluated once \u2014 the honest number\nNo improvement on test \u2192 NO proposal written",
   "lineHeight": 1.25
  },
